{
  "texts": [
    "Beyond just making the vocabulary accessible, they provide context for everything in each news story, so kids can understand what's going on, and why.",
    "In the curriculum connections they encourage kids to think critically not only about the story itself, but about the way the story is presented.",
    "Politics, Arts, Entertainment, Science & Technology, Environment, Animals, Health, Sports, etc.",
    "Not Applicable 13 Time for Kids Authentic, age-appropriate news for kids and valuable resources for teachers and families.",
    "Time for Kids is published in four grade-based editions: K-1, 2, 3-6, and 5-6."
  ]
}